description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 45, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 135, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Nine Lives for East, 5 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10453-59590-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [135 Votes, Top 15% Score]
